<title>USA: Informix backs revenue recognition policy.</title>
<headline>Informix backs revenue recognition policy.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif. 1997-05-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Informix Corp said its revenue recognition policy is in accordance with U.S. Generally Accepted (GAAP).</p>
<p>The company said analyst and media reports have questioned the policy.</p>
<p>Informix, which earlier reported a first quarter loss, also said the company's independent auditors have issued an unqualified opinion on its 1996 financial statements.</p>
